text: Eka chuma gi lowo, gi nyinyo, gi fedha gi dhahabu notore mong始injore matindo tindo, kendo negilokore machal gi mihudhi molwar kar dino cham e ndalo oro. Yamo nobiro moywerogi oko duto, maonge kata buru matin mane odong始. To Lwanda mane otuomo kido mochweno nolokore got marang始ongo kendo nopong始o piny duto.
